{"id":"guide/i18n-optional","title":"Optional practices","contents":"\n\n\n<div class=\"github-links\">\n  <a href=\"https://github.com/ng-docs/angular-cn/edit/aio/aio/content/guide/i18n-optional.md?message=docs%3A%20請簡述你的修改...\" aria-label=\"提供編輯建議\" title=\"提供編輯建議\"><i class=\"material-icons\" aria-hidden=\"true\" role=\"img\">mode_edit</i></a>\n</div>\n\n\n<div class=\"content\">\n  <h1 id=\"optional-practices\" translation-result=\"on\">可選做法<a title=\"Link to this heading\" class=\"header-link\" aria-hidden=\"true\" href=\"guide/i18n-optional#optional-practices\"><i class=\"material-icons\">link</i></a></h1><h1 translation-origin=\"off\" id=\"optional-practices\">Optional practices<a title=\"Link to this heading\" class=\"header-link\" aria-hidden=\"true\" href=\"guide/i18n-optional#optional-practices\"><i class=\"material-icons\">link</i></a></h1>\n\n<p translation-result=\"on\">在特殊情況下，需要以下做法。</p><p translation-origin=\"off\">In special cases, the following practices are required.</p>\n\n<ul>\n<li>\n<p translation-result=\"on\">透過設定 <a href=\"api/core/LOCALE_ID\" title=\"LOCALE_ID | Core - API | Angular\"><code>LOCALE_ID</code></a> 標記來<a href=\"guide/i18n-optional-manual-source-locale\" title=\"Optional practice: Set the source locale manually | Angular\">手動設定源語言環境</a>。</p><p translation-origin=\"off\"><a href=\"guide/i18n-optional-manual-source-locale\" title=\"Optional practice: Set the source locale manually | Angular\">Set the source locale manually</a> by setting the <a href=\"api/core/LOCALE_ID\" title=\"LOCALE_ID | Core - API | Angular\"><code>LOCALE_ID</code></a> token.</p>\n\n</li>\n<li>\n<p translation-result=\"on\"><a href=\"guide/i18n-optional-import-global-variants\" title=\"Optional practice: Import global variants of the locale data | Angular\">匯入語言環境資料的全域變數</a> 用作額外的語言環境資料。</p><p translation-origin=\"off\"><a href=\"guide/i18n-optional-import-global-variants\" title=\"Optional practice: Import global variants of the locale data | Angular\">Import global variants of the locale data</a> for extra locale data.</p>\n\n</li>\n<li>\n<p translation-result=\"on\">如果你需要對匹配翻譯進行更多控制，可以<a href=\"guide/i18n-optional-manage-marked-text\" title=\"Optional practice: Manage marked text with custom IDs | Angular\">用自訂 ID 管理標記文字</a>。</p><p translation-origin=\"off\"><a href=\"guide/i18n-optional-manage-marked-text\" title=\"Optional practice: Manage marked text with custom IDs | Angular\">Manage marked text with custom IDs</a> if you require more control over matching translations.</p>\n\n</li>\n</ul>\n<!-- links -->\n<!-- external links -->\n<!-- end links -->\n\n  <div class=\"reviewed\">最後複查時間： 2021/9/15</div>\n</div>\n\n\n<!-- links to this doc:\n-->\n<!-- links from this doc:\n - api/core/LOCALE_ID\n - guide/i18n-optional#optional-practices\n - guide/i18n-optional-import-global-variants\n - guide/i18n-optional-manage-marked-text\n - guide/i18n-optional-manual-source-locale\n - https://github.com/ng-docs/angular-cn/edit/aio/aio/content/guide/i18n-optional.md?message=docs%3A%20請簡述你的修改...\n-->"}